  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00001",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "赵匡胤上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00002",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "浪荡走天涯，心事乱如麻。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00003",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "时不至来运不通，撒却爹娘走关东。酒醉杀坏御乐女，今日方知路途穷。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00004",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "在下姓赵名匡胤，表字玄郎。只因在家闯下大祸，俺爹娘修下书信，命我五路探亲。闻得洒金桥有位算命先生，神机妙算，善断人之生死祸福。今日天气晴和，不免催马前行。",
      "text_length": 77
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00005",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "想当初在家时何等闲静，每日里诸般事快乐如心。悔不该大街上错交异姓，他本是卖油汉名唤郑恩。酒醉后杀御乐一十七口，连累了二双亲拿在午门。多亏了众文武一同保奏，天牢内受尽了苦楚万分。普天下画图形捉拿匡胤，不由得俺豪杰胆战心惊。思想起这件事神魂不定，且到那金桥下查点五星。",
      "text_length": 132
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00006",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "赵匡胤下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00007",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "苗训上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00008",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "苗训"
      ],
      "text": "在深山领受了师尊之命，洒金桥开命馆只为真君。招牌上写的是神机妙算，算人间吉凶事不差毫分。这几日坐桥头并无人问，桌案上起灰尘半寸余深。待贫道抱袖内掐指一算，今日里赤须龙要查五星。",
      "text_length": 88
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00009",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "苗训坐。赵匡胤上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00010",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "有豪杰催骏马逶迤前进，又只见那壁厢雾气腾腾。一路上好茶饭何曾用饱，招商店美人儿未饮杯巡。这都是俺玄郎命里造定，今日里一心要查算五星。见一人坐桥头手执书本，但不知看的是哪部古文。见先生神潇洒必有学问，好一似三国中诸葛孔明。俺这里下雕鞍忙施一礼，烦先生算八字多多奉金。",
      "text_length": 132
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00011",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "苗训"
      ],
      "text": "你是要看那八字么？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00012",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "正是。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00013",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "苗训"
      ],
      "text": "那厢请坐，待贫道慢慢讲来。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00014",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "先生请算。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00015",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "苗训"
      ],
      "text": "听了。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00016",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "苗训"
      ],
      "text": "你那里算八字休通姓名，待贫道细说与年月时生。你本是平阳府西洛匡胤，南方的赤须龙降下凡尘。你父亲在朝中为官清正，因此上两条龙一母同生。你不该大街上错交异姓，你不该现原形露出金身。你不该杀御乐一十七口，连累你二双亲险些丧生。这几载时不至浅龙遭困，好一似汉关公暂处曹营。",
      "text_length": 132
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00017",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "皆因我时不至大运不顺，烦先生查算我可有灾星？",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00018",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "苗训"
      ],
      "text": "我算你戍己土缺少水饮，百日内必要见血光灾星。一不可古庙内夜与鬼混，二不可三皇殿毁像欺神。三不可在华山下棋争论，四不可打五虎结党成群。五不可黄土岗自呈本领，六不可清幽观结拜送行。七不可归家去问安探信，八不可花亭内箭射鱼精。九不可下燕京刺杀刘王，十不可高平关许妹为婚。我算你十件事件件有准，到头来方知我苗训卦灵。",
      "text_length": 154
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00019",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "苗先生算八字自然有准，但不知何年月大展才能？",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00020",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "苗训"
      ],
      "text": "我算你四十岁才通大运，到陈桥兵变时独霸为君。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00021",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "尊先生你说话需要言准，这件事犯王法不可奉承。我日后果然有天大福分，那时节封你为开国元勋。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00022",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "苗训"
      ],
      "text": "谢主龙恩！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00023",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "赵匡胤"
      ],
      "text": "洒金桥辞别了先生苗训，我把你普天下到处传闻。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00024",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "赵匡胤下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00025",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "苗训"
      ],
      "text": "臣送驾。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00026",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "苗训"
      ],
      "text": "在金桥受过了真主加封，到后来我也是开国元勋。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02008026_e00027",
      "play_id": "02008026",
      "scene_id": "02008026_s02",
